  "text": "On the other hand, when ∆ is any of these polytopes (i)-(iii), the number r is equal to 2; thus, from Theorem 1 and the result of [CITATION_1] , it follows that condition j R j = 0 is satisfied by all the mass linear pairs (∆, b). This fact can also be proved by direct calculation (Propositions 14, 18 and 21). So, Theorem 1, together with these Propositions, generalize the result proved in [CITATION_2] .",
